OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome cloudy areas with mist and
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain affecting higher
OL,7,Fground. Turning sunnier for most by
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, especially further
OL,9,Feast. Feeling very warm by afternoon.
OL,10,FCooler over the Cheviots and North
OL,11,FPennines, with cloud probably
OL,12,Flingering here longest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA fine night with mostly
OL,15,Fclear skies across the region. Some
OL,16,Fcloud likely over higher ground,
OL,17,Fespecially later in the night. Winds
OL,18,Fremaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
